                    <div class="cms-card-content">
                        <div>
                            <span class="cms-card-subtitle">담임목사 3분 설교 Pastor's 3-Min Sermon</span>
                            <h3 class="cms-card-title">담임목사 3분 설교</h3>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cms-card-arrow">
                        <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
