    <!-- ━━━ CHURCH SCHOOL ━━━ -->
    <section class="cms-school">
        <!-- blurred background -->
        <div class="cms-school-bg-wrap">
            <div class="cms-school-bg" style="background-image: url('/UserData/itaewonmc/Layouts/itaewonmc_Layout/images/asset_2.png');"></div>
        </div>
        <!-- grain texture overlay -->
        <div class="cms-school-grain">
            <svg width="100%" height="100%" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <filter id="churchSchoolGrain">
                    <feTurbulence type="fractalNoise" baseFrequency="0.35" numOctaves="2" stitchTiles="stitch" />
                </filter>
                <rect width="100%" height="100%" filter="url(#churchSchoolGrain)" />
            </svg>
        </div>
        <!-- dark overlay for text readability -->
        <div class="cms-school-overlay"></div>
        <div class="cms-container cms-school-content">
            <div class="cms-fade-up" data-delay="0">
                <h2 class="cms-school-title">
                    다음세대를 위한 이태원교회 교회학교
                </h2>
                <p class="cms-school-desc">
                    다음세대가 신앙 안에서 건강하게 자라가도록 돕는 공동체입니다.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="cms-school-grid">
                <div class="cms-fade-up" data-delay="0">
                    <div class="cms-school-card">
                        <div class="cms-school-card-icon"><img src="/UserData/itaewonmc/Layouts/itaewonmc_Layout/images/asset_3.svg" alt="영·유치부" width="72" height="72" /></div>
                        <h4 class="cms-school-card-title">영·유치부</h4>
                        <p class="cms-school-card-desc">영아와 유아가 부모와 함께 예배하며
신앙의 첫 걸음을 시작하는 공동체입니다.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cms-fade-up" data-delay="120">
                    <div class="cms-school-card">
                        <div class="cms-school-card-icon"><img src="/UserData/itaewonmc/Layouts/itaewonmc_Layout/images/asset_4.svg" alt="아동부" width="72" height="72" /></div>
                        <h4 class="cms-school-card-title">아동부(다윗 아동부)</h4>
                        <p class="cms-school-card-desc">말씀을 통해 하나님을 배우고,
신앙의 기초를 다져가는 공동체입니다.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cms-fade-up" data-delay="240">
                    <div class="cms-school-card">
                        <div class="cms-school-card-icon"><img src="/UserData/itaewonmc/Layouts/itaewonmc_Layout/images/asset_5.svg" alt="학생부" width="72" height="72" /></div>
                        <h4 class="cms-school-card-title">학생부(다니엘 학생부)</h4>
                        <p class="cms-school-card-desc">청소년 시기에 하나님을 인격적으로 만나고,
신앙과 삶을 연결해 가도록 돕는 공동체입니다.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="cms-fade-up" data-delay="360">
                    <div class="cms-school-card">
                        <div class="cms-school-card-icon"><img src="/UserData/itaewonmc/Layouts/itaewonmc_Layout/images/asset_6.svg" alt="청년부" width="72" height="72" /></div>
                        <h4 class="cms-school-card-title">청년부(갈렙 청년부)</h4>
                        <p class="cms-school-card-desc">예수 그리스도를 삶의 중심에 두고 살아가는
청년들이 함께 예배하고 교제하는 공동체입니다.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

